[% META title = "Our Bee Products" %]
[% PageVersion = 'Bmaster/products.tt,v 0.02 2026/03/17 shanta Exp shanta' %]
[% IF debug_mode == 1 %]
    [% PageVersion %]
[% END %]

<div class="app-container">

    <div class="page-header">
        <h1>Our Bee Products</h1>
        <p class="page-subtitle">Pure, natural products from healthy, well-managed hives.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="content-container">
        <div class="content-primary">

            <div class="app-section">
                <p>We offer a variety of bee products, each carefully harvested and processed to ensure the highest quality. Explore our range below.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="app-section">
                <div class="content-section">
                    <h2>Honey</h2>
                    <p>Our honey is 100% pure, raw, and unfiltered, harvested from our healthy hives. Rich in flavor and packed with natural enzymes, antioxidants, and natural goodness.</p>
                    <p><a href="/BMaster/honey">Learn about our honey production</a></p>
                </div>

                <div class="content-section">
                    <h2>Bee Pollen</h2>
                    <p>Bee pollen is a superfood packed with proteins, vitamins, and minerals. Harvested from our hives and carefully dried at low temperatures to preserve its full nutritional content.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="content-section">
                    <h2>Beeswax</h2>
                    <p>Our beeswax is pure and natural — harvested from the comb cappings during honey extraction. Ideal for making candles, cosmetics, wood polish, and leather treatments.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="content-section">
                    <h2>Propolis</h2>
                    <p>Propolis is a resinous substance collected by bees from tree buds, used to seal and protect the hive. Known for its antimicrobial and anti-inflammatory properties, it is available in tincture and raw form.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="content-section">
                    <h2>Royal Jelly</h2>
                    <p>Royal jelly is the nutrient-rich secretion produced by worker bees and fed exclusively to queen larvae. Harvested carefully from queen-rearing cells and refrigerated to preserve potency.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="app-section">
                <h2>Advertise Your Products and Services</h2>
                <div class="content-section">
                    <p>Members of the BMaster community can list their own bee products and services here. Contact us to learn about adding your listing.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="page-footer">
                <div class="footer-actions">
                    <a href="/BMaster" class="btn btn-secondary">Back to BMaster Home</a>
                </div>
            </div>

        </div>
    </div>

</div>
